description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a skilled Freelance Video Editor to join our team on a contract basis. You will be producing high-quality product videos for client and marketing purposes, helping to showcase our offerings effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You‚Äôll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edit and assemble recorded raw material into a polished and professional video product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trim footage segments and put together the sequence of the film.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Input music, dialogues, graphics, and effects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create rough and final cuts while ensuring logical sequencing and smooth running.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with our creative team to ensure alignment with project goals and brand standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously discover and implement new editing technologies and industry‚Äôs best practices to maximize efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven work experience as a Video Editor with a strong portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in video editing software such as Adobe Premiere Pro, Final Cut Pro, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of timing, motivation, and continuity in filmmaking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and manage multiple projects simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and ability to collaborate with a remote team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and a keen eye for visual aesthetics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated and a problem solver with excellent time management skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of motion graphics and visual effects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with color grading and sound design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with various video formats and compression techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To Apply:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please submit your resume and a link to a portfolio of your design work. Applications without portfolios will not be considered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will be paying at a rate of USD $5.50 per hour.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: OneLocal pays freelancers using Direct Deposit. Please only apply for this position if you can get paid via Direct Deposit. Thank you!&lt;/p&gt;
